channel.title: Can Anyone Help me - Custom Items
channel.description:
I added a custom item. My client freezes when I loaded it, even though I said 'add model NAME' and it added correctly.
I think I have incorrect ints, and I get an error with another class, here's the error with other class:
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/6074/errorst9.png[/img]
I remember reading someone saying how they add something to this class to make their items work (they weren't talking to me, I was just reading a thread, so I can't reach them) Hopefully someone knows what to add?
Also, I noticed that in the already added models to my client, when I extract them, the file inside's name is different?
So if it's name is 4201.gz, and I extract it, the file inside could be called 19052 (random number)... Wtf is up with that? When I gzip my file, it stays with the same name...
